properties = [property1, property2]
property_list = ""

for property in properties:
    address = property['location']['address']['line']
    city = property['location']['address']['city']
    state = property['location']['address']['state']
    postal_code = property['location']['address']['postal_code']
    price = property['list_price']
    bedrooms = property['bedrooms']
    bathrooms = property['bathrooms']
    
    property_info = f"Address: {address}, {city}, {state} {postal_code}\n"
    property_info += f"Price: ${price}\n"
    property_info += f"Bedrooms: {bedrooms}\n"
    property_info += f"Bathrooms: {bathrooms}\n\n"
    
    property_list += property_info

property_list
